                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-761-18630511 t18630511-761-punishment-108"></join>Four Years' Penal Servitude each</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">There were several other similar indictments against the prisoners.</hi>
